data.title: Tom Lee Cuts Bitcoin Price Prediction to $100K, Says Tether’s Gold Buying Lifts BTC Outlook
data.description: Tom Lee has lowered his year-end Bitcoin target from $250,000 to “above $100,000." Lee says Tether's gold buying will help set a higher long-term price ...
data.keywords: Tom Lee, Bitcoin price, Tether, price of Bitcoin, gold buying
